title: Through Being Cool Vegan Baking Co.
description: Vegan bakery offering both sweet as well savory baked goods including cupcakes, scones, fried doughnuts, pizza buns, pretzels, and more. Has a coffee bar and also sells a range of ready-made as well frozen meals for take home like vegan mac and cheese, lasagna, cabbage rolls, sandwiches, and ravioli. Lansdowne subway station.
